44:24.195 --> 44:27.032
* Hey-ay-ay *

44:27.065 --> 44:29.067
WOMAN:
This is our story.

44:29.100 --> 44:31.369
* Can't stop me now *

44:31.402 --> 44:33.471
* Can't stop me now *

44:33.504 --> 44:35.506
